(def profilePic (r/atom nil))

(defn emptyPhoto [photo]
  (nil? @photo))

(defn ipfs-add-image [filename file-data]
  (let [blob (js/Blob. (clj->js [file-data]) #js {:type "image/*"})]
    (ifiles/add blob {:path filename}
                (fn [err files]
                  (println [err files])))))

(defn submitProfile [name photo details]
    (println (.-name @photo))
    (let [blob (js/Blob. (clj->js [@photo]) #js {:type "image/*"})]
      (ifiles/add blob {:path (.-name @photo)}
                  (fn [err files]
                    (if err
                      (println (str "err: " err))
                      (let [hash (. (. js/JSON parse files) -Hash)]
                        (println "files: " files)
                        (println "hash: " hash)))))))

                      (println ""files: "" files)

    """

                         (fn [error txHash] ;; callback

(defn testPage [{:keys [details step]}]
  (init-ipfs {:host "http://127.0.0.1:5001"})
  [:div
   [:div
    [typography
     {:variant "h6"
      :component "div"}
     "3. Upload a profile picture"]

    [:label
     {:html-for "upload-image" :style {:margin "0 auto"}}
     [:input
      {:accept "image/*"
       :id "upload-image"
       :type "file"
       :style {:display "none"}
       :on-change #(let [uploaded (-> % .-target .-files (aget 0))] (reset! profilePic uploaded))}]
     [icon-button
      {:component "span"}
      [add-a-photo-sharp]]]

    [typography
     {:variant "h6"
      :component "div"
      :sx {:color (if (emptyPhoto profilePic)  "#d32f2f" "#070707")
           :font-size "12px"
           :font-weight "500"}}
     (if (emptyPhoto profilePic) "no photo uploaded" (.-name @profilePic))]]

   [:div
    [button
     {:variant "contained"
      :disable-elevation true
      :on-click #(submitProfile name profilePic details)}
     "Submit"]]])
